name: Kyle Krafka
body:
### About Me
I am currently a software engineer, specializing in computer vision and deep learning, for [Project Wing](https://www.solveforx.com/wing/) at [X](https://www.solveforx.com/) (previously Google X). I recently graduated from the University of Georgia in December of 2015. My dissertation applied deep learning to eye tracking on cell phones.

### Contact
Feel free to reach out to me via kkrafka at uga.edu. Have a great day!
